	Chaos 
		The English word vs the mathematical field
	Iteration 
		Think of it as feedback
	Nonlinear 
		The Whole is greater than the sum of its parts
	Dynamical System 
		A changing system that obeys fixed rules
	Fractal 
		Infinitely fractured, self-similar geometric object
	Attractor 
		Where things tend to end up after many iterations

